<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Session Reactivation Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #dd163b, #ff5e62);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .session-details {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Session Reactivation Request</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{ coach.prenom }} {{ coach.nom }},</p>

        <p>A user has requested to reactivate one of your expired gaming sessions. Here are the details:</p>

        <div class="session-details">
            <h3>Session Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Game:</strong> {{ session.game }}</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{ session.dureeSession }}</p>
            <p><strong>Price:</strong> {{ session.prix }} â‚¬</p>
            <p><strong>Created on:</strong> {{ session.dateCreation|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
        </div>

        <p>Please review this request and consider reactivating the session if possible.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from your Gaming Platform</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>